					"value": "A quick way to trigger this dialog would be destroying the pillar at 284; 24; 342 (S_CHA_OUTSIDE_Fissure_Boulder) and opening the hole at the chapel, then walk throught the main locked door and kill Andorn before he calls for help. Once they are in their positions AD will trigger."
